{"tid":610173,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"植物人應該點過冇得r痕既日子","createTime":"2018-03-29T16:26:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T04:21:23.000Z","uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eadae684b7018bb13773caf13050b6df90e44b01","tid":610173,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T16:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60de4cc77ed15fbd10ae22e8f89e2724708aea40","tid":610173,"uid":56240,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T16:27:30.000Z","msg":"不要暗戀，去強姦。人生沒有那麼多時間給你演內心戲。愛她就去搞她，喜歡就去強姦。表白有什麼用還是會被拒絕。追不到就下藥，翻臉就殺了她。大不了就被殺，你連投胎都不敢還好意思說愛她。投胎長大之後找到她繼續強姦，強姦到讓她開始懷疑自己的人生，讓她覺得她人生的意義就是被你強姦。"},{"pid":"7e76c31952af1f03b0973d0cb26dcc7ecb96e761","tid":610173,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T16:27:46.000Z","msg":"植物人既感官其實仲接唔接收到刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406dd2cac7c2755ce5a6b400658588d1c0ff4b76","tid":610173,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T16:30:13.000Z","msg":"植物人會覺得痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe13206824f6b24dc51bc45393a066254e05cdb","tid":610173,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"406dd2cac7c2755ce5a6b400658588d1c0ff4b76","tid":610173,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T16:30:13.000Z","msg":"植物人會覺得痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T16:39:13.000Z","msg":"控制唔到但係有感覺🤔"},{"pid":"8c56fd6ff7a232519b3be8e5fad4a31029b9df73","tid":610173,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbe13206824f6b24dc51bc45393a066254e05cdb","tid":610173,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"406dd2cac7c2755ce5a6b400658588d1c0ff4b76","tid":610173,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-